{"tid":656181,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過夜遊大帽山撞野?","createTime":"2018-05-07T04:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T02:09:16.000Z","uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"6343fc65cf7a55925361ce9709376dae913fc957","tid":656181,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的,早2日同個FRD同條女去左果度露營,諗住沿車路上行上山頂睇流星雨,點知好大霧乜都睇唔到,能見度我諗得4-5米,去到觀景台有2粒大石果個位置咁上下,個石頭上面寫左D佛經D咒語咁,女朋友係呢個時候無喇喇喊,我見唔對路馬上拉佢走(女朋友本身有陰陽眼底),之後番番去營地時問佢見到咩話見到多左個黑影伏左係我同我個FRD中間,但得佢見到,見我地無咩反應咁,所以嚇到喊。後尾上網GOOGLE下先知原來大帽山好猛,好多鬼故。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似經歷?"},{"pid":"f07153dc23c68fa7b83296c76a41ebcc6a42c65a","tid":656181,"uid":147233,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"好多年前除夕渣車上去 旺過旺角"},{"pid":"7e00dd47fd601e804cc76ee3a9273bd59a762475","tid":656181,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f07153dc23c68fa7b83296c76a41ebcc6a42c65a","tid":656181,"uid":147233,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:11:49.000Z","msg":"好多年前除夕渣車上去 旺過旺角"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8870ac78e436b4a878b25449612ea9ece11642ef","tid":656181,"uid":157973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"獅子山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0e2144b8ee3e4ac44d4eb7e572ed98ae0341ce","tid":656181,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:43:50.000Z","msg":"冇搞你咪算囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640d80dbb26aac808c639b967b8048d405ec40d1","tid":656181,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"06d43021f4953a8621121201dbb0599cfc9d2158","tid":656181,"uid":80565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"咁樓主有無事？發燒，周身唔舒服？"},{"pid":"09c95ff10fb387232a7d3579f5eb4befed001c41","tid":656181,"uid":42586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"全香港有邊到唔猛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2d38a3620b32bf029c361a166adfba134a992c","tid":656181,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"more"},{"pid":"a781dfba97e445f7cc2c0113371086aa04a425a8","tid":656181,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"據網絡傳聞，一對情侶駕車到大帽山聊天，一直聊到凌晨二點，男生在車裡呼呼大睡，而女生因凍得無法入睡。不久，突然在遠處傳出像腳步聲的嘈雜聲音，隨後又傳來像開槍的聲音，她害怕得閉上眼睛，然而，那些槍聲越來越接近她們，於是她張開眼一望，聲音突然間停了，嚇然見到一個前額束上紅點白布，手持一把刀，好似日本軍人，但嘴臉模糊的人影站在左邊的車窗外，他舉起手似要砍下來，但砍下來時是沒有聲音的。她怕得大叫並不斷拍醒旁邊的男朋友。他一醒來，那日本軍人便消失了。當她正要細說事發經過時，她們從側鏡見到後面有火光，兩團火球在不遠處凌空的移轉。他們隨即駕車離去，怎料那兩火球一直尾隨，一直到山腳公廁的位置才消失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.d18hk.com/%E6%95%85%E4%BB%94/%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%89%E9%AC%BC%E6%95%85-%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%BD%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%BA_1104/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.d18hk.com%2F%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BB%2594%2F%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25AC%25BC%25E6%2595%2585-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%25BD%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA_1104%2F&d=w0NGSwCg9T%2FhjTbcvAW1Sf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a3368019\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.d18hk.com/%E6%95%85%E4%BB%94/%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%89%E9%AC%BC%E6%95%85-%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%BD%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%BA_1104/</a>"},{"pid":"9ac7ea1c0cb9477dc7faaabf6177849d133f2307","tid":656181,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:26:29.000Z","msg":"有冇燒d野呀臨走"},{"pid":"2c0184d63f37fe29b5f9d5c234cb3483d918922d","tid":656181,"uid":887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ac7ea1c0cb9